         |                 ^
      18 |     
      19 |     return { message: `Hello user ${user.id}` };
      20 |   }

      at MyController.getData (my.controller.ts:17:17)
      at Object.<anonymous> (my.controller.spec.ts:44:22)
```
As you can see the logger is undefined which was provided properly.


